sources.title: Western | Desert Justice (1960) | Michael Landon, Lorne Greene | Bonanza TV Classic
sources.description:
Adam and Hoss try to help a ranch hand (Wesley Lau) who's being taken to California for trial by a brutal U.S. marshal (Claude Akins), but things are not as they first seem.
 
Director: Lewis Allen
Writer: Donald S. Sanford
Stars: Dan Blocker, Michael Landon, Lorne Greene 
Genres: Bonanza, Classics, Cult, TV, Western
